summary: I honestly dont know how I feel about this whole J.J Abrams/Spider-Man series. Like the way Marvel was hyping it didnt help and...
body: I honestly dont know how I feel about this whole J.J Abrams/Spider-Man series. Like the way Marvel was hyping it didnt help and it seems his son is going to be writing for the most part while his name was slapped on for marketing. I have nothing against Abrams or his son but was someone really wanting this? Like Marvel already has a shit ton of Spider titles already so do we need another one?

summary: Michael Giacchino Releases "Far From Home Suite Home" Ahead of This Summer's "Spider-Man: Far From Home"
title: Michael Giacchino Releases "Far From Home Suite Home" Ahead of This Summer's "Spider-Man: Far From Home"
body:
Michael Giacchino Releases “Far From Home Suite Home” Ahead of This Summer’s “Spider-Man: Far From Home”

Today, we got an exciting new piece of Marvel! With Spider-Man: Far From Home hitting theaters in just a few short weeks, we’re getting so excited to see one of our favorite heroes hit the big screen again. This morning, Michael Giacchino took to Twitter to announce that the “Far From Home Suite Home” is officially here!

Giacchino had previously stated that he has wanted the theme to grow more…
